 &lt;img src="https://blog-pic-ck.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/posts/zh/ml-math-derivations/19-%e7%a5%9e%e7%bb%8f%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e4%b8%8e%e5%8f%8d%e5%90%91%e4%bc%a0%e6%92%ad/illustration_1.png" alt="机器学习数学推导（19）：神经网络与反向传播 —— 图示" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="content-image">
 
